title: Tex Tubb's Taco Palace
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Take-out, Mexican, Tex-Mex, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tex-Mexican restaurant with marked vegan choices including nachos and vegan queso in the appetizers section. Many items on the menu can be made vegan when requested. Owned by the same restaurant group as Monty's Blue Plate Diner down the street, which also has vegan items on their menu.
